import React from 'react'
import Navigation from "../Navigation"
import Header4 from "../All_pages/Header4"
import ContactMe from "../All_pages/ContactMe"
import ContactDetail from "../All_pages/ContactDetail"
import Footer from "../Footer"

export const ContactUs = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Navigation/>
        <Header4/>
        <ContactMe/>
        <ContactDetail/>
        <Footer/>
        </>
    )
}
export default ContactUs
